ReadCollection1

data.name: ReadCollection2
data.value: select COLL_ID, APPLIED_TO_CD, COLL_DT, ADJ_IND, CONCURRENT_IND, CRT_TYPE, CST_ID, CRV_ID, CRD_ID, OBG_ID, CSP_NUMBER, CPA_TYPE, OTR_ID, OTR_TYPE, OTY_ID, COLL_ADJ_DT, CREATED_TMST, OB_TRN_AMT, PGM_APPLD_TO from CKT_COLLECTION with(readuncommitted) where (@otyId = OTY_ID) and (@otrType = OTR_TYPE) and (@otrId = OTR_ID) and (@cpaType = CPA_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (@obgId = OBG_ID) and (APPLIED_TO_CD in ('C', 'A')) and (ADJ_IND = 'Y') and (CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst) and (COLL_ADJ_DT > @collAdjDt)

data.name: ReadCollection4
data.value: select COLL_ID, APPLIED_TO_CD, COLL_DT, ADJ_IND, CONCURRENT_IND, CRT_TYPE, CST_ID, CRV_ID, CRD_ID, OBG_ID, CSP_NUMBER, CPA_TYPE, OTR_ID, OTR_TYPE, OTY_ID, COLL_ADJ_DT, CREATED_TMST, OB_TRN_AMT, PGM_APPLD_TO from CKT_COLLECTION with(readuncommitted) where (APPLIED_TO_CD in ('A', 'C')) and (@otyId = OTY_ID) and (@otrType = OTR_TYPE) and (@otrId = OTR_ID) and (@cpaType = CPA_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (@obgId = OBG_ID) and ( ( (ADJ_IND = 'N') and (CREATED_TMST > @createdTmst) ) or ( (ADJ_IND = 'Y') and (CREATED_TMST < @createdTmst) and (COLL_ADJ_DT > @collAdjDt) ) )

data.name: ReadDebtAdjustment1
data.value: select top(1) OBG_GENERATED_ID, CSP_NUMBER, CPA_TYPE, OB_TRN_ID, OB_TRN_TYP, OB_TRN_AMT, DEBT_ADJ_TYP, DEB_ADJ_DT, CREATED_TMST, CSP_SUP_NUMBER, CPA_SUP_TYPE, OTY_TYPE from CKT_OB_TRN where (@cpaType = CPA_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (DEBT_ADJ_TYP = 'D') and (DEB_ADJ_DT > @debAdjDt)

data.name: ReadDebtAdjustment2
data.value: select distinct T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.DEBT_ADJ_TYP, T1.DEB_ADJ_DT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE from CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN_RLN T2 with(readuncommitted) on (@otyType = T1.OTY_TYPE) and (@obgGeneratedId = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (@cspNumber = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (@cpaType = T1.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.DEB_ADJ_DT > @debAdjDt) and (T1.OTY_TYPE = T2.OTY_TYPE_SECONDARY) and (T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T2.OTR_TYPE) and (T1.OB_TRN_ID = T2.OTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T2.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T2.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (@otyTypePrimary = T2.OTY_TYPE_PRIMARY) and (@otrPType = T2.OTR_P_TYPE) and (@otrPGeneratedId = T2.OTR_P_GENERATED_ID) and (@cpaPType = T2.CPA_P_TYPE) and (@cspPNumber = T2.CSP_P_NUMBER) and (@obgPGeneratedId = T2.OBG_P_GENERATED_ID)

data.name: ReadDebtObligationObligationTypeDebtDetail1
data.value: select distinct T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE, T2.PRIM_SEC_CD, T2.CREATED_TMST, T2.ORD_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS, T4.DUE_DT, T4.BAL_DUE_AMT, T4.CVRD_PRD_START_DT, T4.PRECNVRSN_PGM_CD, T4.CREATED_TMST from CKT_OB_TYPE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OBLIGATION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T6 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN_RLN T5 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.OTY_TYPE = T5.OTY_TYPE_PRIMARY) and (T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T5.OTR_P_TYPE) and (T1.OB_TRN_ID = T5.OTR_P_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_P_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_P_NUMBER) and (T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T5.OBG_P_GENERATED_ID) and (@cpaSupType = T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE) and (@cspSupNumber = T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER) and (T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst) on (T6.OTY_TYPE = T5.OTY_TYPE_SECONDARY) and (T6.OB_TRN_TYP = T5.OTR_TYPE) and (T6.OB_TRN_ID = T5.OTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T6.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_TYPE) and (T6.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_NUMBER) and (T6.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T5.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T6.DEBT_ADJ_TYP = 'D') and (T6.DEB_ADJ_DT > @debAdjDt) on (T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID = T6.OTY_TYPE) and (T2.OB_ID = T6.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T6.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.CPA_TYPE = T6.CPA_TYPE) and (@cpaType = T2.CPA_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID = T1.OTY_TYPE) and (T2.OB_ID = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE) and (T2.PRIM_SEC_CD <> 'S') and (T2.ORD_TYP_CD <> 'I') on T3.DEBT_TYP_ID = T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID join CKT_DEBT_DTL T4 with(readuncommitted) on (T4.BAL_DUE_AMT = 0) and (T1.OTY_TYPE = T4.OTY_TYPE) and (T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T4.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T4.OTR_TYPE) and (T1.OB_TRN_ID = T4.OTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER) and ( ( (T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS = 'A') and (T4.DUE_DT < dateadd(month, - 1, cast(@debAdjDt as date))) ) or (T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS in ('M', 'N')) )

data.name: ReadDebtObligationObligationTypeDebtDetail2
data.value: select distinct T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE, T2.PRIM_SEC_CD, T2.CREATED_TMST, T2.ORD_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS, T4.DUE_DT, T4.BAL_DUE_AMT, T4.CVRD_PRD_START_DT, T4.PRECNVRSN_PGM_CD, T4.CREATED_TMST from CKT_OB_TYPE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OBLIGATION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_COLLECTION T5 with(readuncommitted) on (T1.OTY_TYPE = T5.OTY_ID) and (T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T5.OTR_TYPE) and (T1.OB_TRN_ID = T5.OTR_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T5.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T5.CSP_NUMBER) and (T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T5.OBG_ID) and (T5.APPLIED_TO_CD in ('C', 'A')) and (T5.ADJ_IND = 'N') and (T5.CREATED_TMST > @createdTmst) and (@cpaSupType = T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE) and (@cspSupNumber = T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER) and (T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst) on (@cpaType = T2.CPA_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID = T1.OTY_TYPE) and (T2.OB_ID = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE) and (T2.PRIM_SEC_CD <> 'S') and (T2.ORD_TYP_CD <> 'I') on T3.DEBT_TYP_ID = T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID join CKT_DEBT_DTL T4 with(readuncommitted) on (T4.BAL_DUE_AMT = 0) and (T1.OTY_TYPE = T4.OTY_TYPE) and (T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T4.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T4.OTR_TYPE) and (T1.OB_TRN_ID = T4.OTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER) and ( ( (T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS = 'A') and (T4.DUE_DT < dateadd(month, - 1, cast(@date as date))) ) or (T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS in ('M', 'N')) )

data.name: ReadDebtObligationObligationTypeDebtDetail3
data.value: select T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID, T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_TYPE, T1.OB_TRN_ID, T1.OB_TRN_TYP, T1.OB_TRN_AMT, T1.CREATED_TMST, T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER, T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE, T1.OTY_TYPE, T2.PRIM_SEC_CD, T2.CREATED_TMST, T2.ORD_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CD, T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS, T4.DUE_DT, T4.BAL_DUE_AMT, T4.CVRD_PRD_START_DT, T4.PRECNVRSN_PGM_CD, T4.CREATED_TMST from CKT_OB_TYPE T3 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OBLIGATION T2 with(readuncommitted) join CKT_OB_TRN T1 with(readuncommitted) on (@cpaType = T2.CPA_TYPE) and (@cspNumber = T2.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID = T1.OTY_TYPE) and (T2.OB_ID = T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T2.CSP_NUMBER = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (T2.CPA_TYPE = T1.CPA_TYPE) and (@cpaSupType = T1.CPA_SUP_TYPE) and (@cspSupNumber = T1.CSP_SUP_NUMBER) and (T2.PRIM_SEC_CD <> 'S') and (T2.ORD_TYP_CD <> 'I') and (T1.CREATED_TMST <= @createdTmst) on T3.DEBT_TYP_ID = T2.DTY_GENERATED_ID join CKT_DEBT_DTL T4 with(readuncommitted) on (T4.BAL_DUE_AMT > 0) and (T1.OTY_TYPE = T4.OTY_TYPE) and (T1.OBG_GENERATED_ID = T4.OBG_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.OB_TRN_TYP = T4.OTR_TYPE) and (T1.OB_TRN_ID = T4.OTR_GENERATED_ID) and (T1.CPA_TYPE = T4.CPA_TYPE) and (T1.CSP_NUMBER = T4.CSP_NUMBER) and ( ( (T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS = 'A') and (T4.DUE_DT < dateadd(month, - 1, cast(@date as date))) ) or (T3.DEBT_TYP_CLASS in ('M', 'N')) )
